ParcellationEntityVersion

https://openminds.ebrains.eu/sands/ParcellationEntityVersion

part of SANDS in version v3 - view as JSON Schema

Required properties are highlighted in bold
propertyvalue
name*descriptiontypeinstruction
versionIdentifier Term or code used to identify the version of something. string Enter the version identifier of this parcellation entity version.
hasAnnotation embedded object AtlasAnnotation Add the atlas annotation which this parcellation entity version defines.
hasParent Reference to a parent object or legal person. linked object array (1 - n) of type:
ParcellationEntity OR
ParcellationEntityVersion 		Add the defined anatomical parent structure (version) for this parcellation entity version, or several if required.
name Word or phrase that constitutes the distinctive designation of a being or thing. string If necessary, enter a version specific name for this parcellation entity version. If left blank, the parcellation entity version will inherit the 'name' of it's corresponding parcellation entity.
ontologyIdentifier Term or code used to identify something or someone registered within a particular ontology. string (format: iri) Enter the internationalized resource identifier (IRI) pointing to the ontological term matching this parcellation entity version.
relationAssessment embedded object array (1 - n) of type:
QualitativeRelationAssessment OR
QuantitativeRelationAssessment 		Add one or several relations of this parcellation entity version to parcellation entity versions of other parcellation terminology versions.
versionInnovation Documentation on what changed in comparison to a previously published form of something. string Enter a short description of the novelties/peculiarities of this parcellation entity version.
*This is the simplified property name - within a metadata instance of this schema (JSON-LD) the properties are extended to map to the openMINDS vocabulary namespace ("https://openminds.ebrains.eu/vocab/PROPERTY_NAME").
